         <div xml:id="bHY6yh-e11270"><!-- p5l4-r10 -->
            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-e11270-Hd1e108">Rubrica 10</head>
            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-e11270-Hd1e111" type="question-title">De laudabiliter morientibus et laudabili fama mortuorum</head>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-e11270-d1e114">
               <lb ed="#V" n="6"/>¶ De laudabiliter morientibus et lau
      <lb ed="#V" n="7" break="no"/>dabili fama mortuorum. Rubrica. 10
    </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-e11270-d1e121">
               <lb ed="#V" n="8"/>Tobie. c. 2. <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-e11270-Qd1e125">hoc pro certo ha
        <lb ed="#V" n="9"/>bet omnis qui colit
        <lb ed="#V" n="10"/>deum quoniam vita eius si in probatio
        <lb ed="#V" n="11" break="no"/>ne fuerit coronabitur.</quote> 
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-e11270-d1e135">
               <lb ed="#V" n="12"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-e11270-Qd1e139">¶ Isocrates in exhortationibus. c. 2 in fi.
        <lb ed="#V" n="13"/>Mori quidem in omnes promulgauit for
        <lb ed="#V" n="14" break="no"/>tuna: bene autem mori proprie natura vir
        <lb ed="#V" n="15" break="no"/>tuosis attribuit. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-e11270-d1e150">
               <lb ed="#V" n="16"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-e11270-Qd1e154">¶ Uirgilius enid. l. 10 circa medium: Stat
        <lb ed="#V" n="17"/>sua cuique dies breue et irreparabile tempus
        <lb ed="#V" n="18"/>Omnibus est vite: sed famam extendere factis:
        <lb ed="#V" n="19"/>Hoc virtutis opus. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-e11270-d1e164">
               <lb ed="#V" n="20"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-e11270-Qd1e168">¶ Tullius phylippicorum vel. 13. et fi. Breuis a
        <lb ed="#V" n="21"/>natura nobis vita data est: at memoria bene redi
        <lb ed="#V" n="22" break="no"/>te vite sempinterna. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-e11270-d1e176"> /
      <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-e11270-Qd1e178"> Idem in oratione pro mar
        <lb ed="#V" n="23" break="no"/>co marcello: Nec hec tua vita dicenda est que
        <lb ed="#V" n="24"/>corpore et spiritu continetur: illa inquam vita est tua
        <lb ed="#V" n="25"/>qua vigebit memoria seculorum omnium: quam po
        <lb ed="#V" n="26"/>steritas alet: quam ipsa eternitas semper tuebitur
        <lb ed="#V" n="27"/>huic tu inseruias: huic te obstentes oportet. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-e11270-d1e192">
               <lb ed="#V" n="28"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-e11270-Qd1e196">¶ Libro sapientie. c. 5. Iusti in perpetuum
        <lb ed="#V" n="29"/>viuent: et apud dominum est merces eorum. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-e11270-d1e202">
               <lb ed="#V" n="30"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-e11270-Qd1e206">¶ Mattheus in euangelio. c. 5. Beati mun
        <lb ed="#V" n="31"/>do corde: quoniam ipsi deum videbunt. Beati
        <lb ed="#V" n="32"/>qui persecutionem patiuntur propter iusti
        <lb ed="#V" n="33" break="no"/>tiam: quoniam ipsorum est regnum celorum. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-e11270-d1e216">
               <lb ed="#V" n="34"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-e11270-Qd1e220">¶ Marcus in euangelio. c. 10. Paruulorum
        <lb ed="#V" n="35"/>est regnum dei. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-e11270-d1e227">
               <lb ed="#V" n="36"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-e11270-Qd1e231">¶ Iohannes in appocalypsi. c. 10. Beati mor
        <lb ed="#V" n="37" break="no"/>tui qui in domino moriuntur. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-e11270-d1e237">
               <lb ed="#V" n="38"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-e11270-Qd1e241">¶ Lex institur. ti. de excusatur. tuto. §. iii. Qui pro
        <lb ed="#V" n="39"/>re publica ceciderunt: in perpetum per glo¬ <!--329.xml-->
        <cb ed="#V" n="b"/>
                  <lb ed="#V" n="40"/>riam viuere intelliguntur. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-e11270-d1e253">
               <lb ed="#V" n="41"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-e11270-Qd1e257">¶ Marcialis cocus vel vndique suscepto. c. 2.
        <lb ed="#V" n="42"/>Tarde vel subito vita recedere nil est.
        <lb ed="#V" n="43"/>Si bene decedas pindare non nihil est. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-e11270-d1e265">
               <lb ed="#V" n="44"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-e11270-Qd1e269">¶ Augustinus in epigrammatibus prosperi:
        <lb ed="#V" n="45"/>50. emp. Mala mors putanda non est: quam
        <lb ed="#V" n="46"/>bonam vita precesserit. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-e11270-d1e277">
               <lb ed="#V" n="47"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-e11270-Qd1e281">¶ Cato capitulo. 5. Felices obeunt quorum
        <lb ed="#V" n="48"/>sine crimine vita est. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-e11270-d1e287">
               <lb ed="#V" n="49"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-e11270-Qd1e291">¶ Bernardus. l. de improbatione viciorum
        <lb ed="#V" n="50"/>c. 9. et fi. Id solum te met post mortem fa
        <lb ed="#V" n="51" break="no"/>ctum beabit:
        <lb ed="#V" n="52"/>Quod bene quod iuste quod recte feceris ipse. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-e11270-d1e302">
               <lb ed="#V" n="53"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-e11270-Qd1e306">¶ Mattheus vindocinensis: de hysto. tobie
        <lb ed="#V" n="54"/>c. 66 et antepenult. Iustus obit nec obit: sed
        <lb ed="#V" n="55"/>abit ab hospite migrans
        <lb ed="#V" n="56"/>Carne: petit patriam delitiasque patris. </quote>
            </p>
         </div>
